  "prompt": "What is the best desk lamp?",
  "response": "The \"best\" desk lamp depends on your specific needs, preferences, and budget. Here are some popular and highly-rated desk lamps across different categories:\n\n### 1. **Best Overall: TaoTronics LED Desk Lamp**\n   - **Features:** Adjustable brightness and color temperature, USB charging port, touch control, eye-caring technology.\n   - **Why It\u2019s Great:** Versatile, energy-efficient, and modern design.\n\n### 2. **Best for Students: BenQ e-Reading LED Desk Lamp**\n   - **Features:** Auto-dimming, wide illumination, adjustable color temperature, built-in ambient light sensor.\n   - **Why It\u2019s Great:** Reduces eye strain, ideal for studying, and customizable settings.\n\n### 3. **Best for Office Work: Philips Hue Play Light Bar**\n   - **Features:** Smart lighting, app control, customizable colors and brightness.\n   - **Why It\u2019s Great:** Integrates with smart home systems, creates ambient lighting, and is stylish.\n\n### 4. **Best Budget Option: Ikea Tertial Work Lamp**\n   - **Features:** Adjustable arm and head, clip-on or clamp mount.\n   - **Why It\u2019s Great:** Affordable, simple, and functional.\n\n### 5. **Best for Design: Anglepoise Type 75 Mini Desk Lamp**\n   - **Features:** Classic design, adjustable arms, high-quality materials.\n   - **Why It\u2019s Great:** Iconic design, durable, and adds a touch of elegance to your workspace.\n\n### 6. **Best Smart Lamp: Xiaomi Mi LED Desk Lamp**\n   - **Features:** Smart app control, adjustable brightness and color temperature, sleek design.\n   - **Why It\u2019s Great:** Affordable smart features, modern look, and user-friendly.\n\n### 7. **Best for Art and Detailed Work: OttLite LED Desk Lamp**\n   - **Features:** TrueColor technology, adjustable brightness, flexible neck.\n   - **Why It\u2019s Great:** Provides true-to-life colors, reduces glare, and is perfect for precision tasks.\n\n### Things to Consider When Choosing a Desk Lamp:\n- **Brightness and Color Temperature:** Adjustable settings help reduce eye strain and adapt to different tasks.\n- **Adjustability:** Look for lamps with flexible necks, arms, or heads for optimal positioning.\n- **Energy Efficiency:** LED lamps are energy-efficient and have a longer lifespan.\n- **Style and Aesthetics:** Choose a lamp that complements your workspace decor.\n- **Additional Features:** USB ports, smart controls, and built-in chargers can add convenience.\n\nUltimately, the best desk lamp for you will depend on how you plan to use it and what features are most important to you.",
  "temperature": 1.0,
